title: Australian Road Rider - April 2016
description:
English | 148 pages | PDF | 45.2 MB





One of Australia's best-selling digital motorcycle magazines, Australian Road Rider is the perfect resource for the motorcyclist who wants to get out and do something with his or her bike. Whether it's a trip to Borneo or a Sunday run up into the hills, ARR covers it all while bringing you news of the latest and greatest machines on two (and sometimes three) wheels. And there are always a few laughs to be had as well
